s":{"howToFix":["Remove the unused media file in the Media pane."],"whyFix":"This media file is not referenced by any control formulas so it is not needed. Removing it will improve performance.","componentType":"app","primaryCategory":"performance","level":"Medium"}},{"id":"app-DataSourceDefaultMaxRowsLimit","messageStrings":{"issue":{"text":"Data row limit for non-delegable queries is more than 500"}},"properties":{"howToFix":["Update 'Data row limit for non-delegable queries' in the advanced app settings."],"whyFix":"A 'data row limit' more than 500 may result in a slower app when running non-delegable queries, because the app will have to process every row itself, rather than running the query on the server.","componentType":"app","primaryCategory":"performance","level":"Medium"}},{"id":"app-ScreenHasManyControls","messageStrings":{"issue":{"text":"Too many controls on a screen"}},"properties":{"howToFix":["Reduce the number of controls on the screen.","Break the app into more screens to reduce the per-screen complexity.","Use components to unify grouped controls that are identical across screens, reducing duplication.","Use galleries to represent a series of repeated similar controls.","Break the app into multiple apps so that each app is small and performant."],"whyFix":"Each control consumes resources, and an app may become slow or unresponsive if a screen has too many controls. The estimated complexity of \"IntakeFormScreen\" is 713, which exceeds the maximum threshold recommended (300).","componentType":"app","primaryCategory":"performance","level":"Medium"}},{"id":"app-InefficientDelayLoading","messageStrings":{"issue":{"text":"Inefficient delay loading"}},"properties":{"howToFix":["Use variables, collections, and navigation context to share state across screens instead."],"whyFix":"Controls that reference controls on other screens can slow down app loading and navigation. Doing this may force the app to load the other screens immediately, rather than waiting until the user navigates to that screen.","componentType":"app","primaryCategory":"performance","level":"Medium"}}]}},"invocations":[{"executionSuccessful":true}],"columnKind":"utf16CodeUnits"}]}